Title: The art of writing structured code 
Date: November 28, 2025
Tag: Programming

<style>
summary {
	font-weight: bold;
	font-size: 20px;
	cursor: pointer;
}

ul {
	display: flex;
	flex-direction: column;
	gap: 0.8rem;
	padding: 0.5rem;
	padding-left: 2rem;
}

pre {
	background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240);
